channel.title: Posts on When Did EG Last Throw?
channel.description: Recent content in Posts on When Did EG Last Throw?

item.title: 4th April 2021
item.description: EG last threw against IG on the 4th of April 2021 at The Singapore Major. After looking confident in Grand Finals with a two game lead, IG managed to make a comeback in game 3 and sweep the next two games.

item.title: 13th March 2020
item.description: EG last threw against OG.Seed on the 13th of March 2020 at Dota Summit 12.

item.title: 16th November 2019
item.description: EG last threw against Team Liquid on the 16th of November 2019. At the MDL Chengdu Major.
